{"view":"article","slug":"f2l-orientation","category":"3x3","subcategory":null,"topDir":"3x3","title":{"en":"F2L Orientation","zh":"F2L色向"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">F2L Orientation</strong></p><p><strong>不再更新</strong></p><p><a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a> orientation refers to S-axis orientation of edge of F2L. For definition of edge orientation, see also \"EO\" page. Mirrors are excluded. For all F2L cases, R*,U*,F2 do not change F2L orientation, but F,F' do. If one can recognize the case and the alg is not bad, solve oriented F2L preferentially to avoid unnecessary rotations.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Edge Position</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Oriented</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Misoriented</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>y/y' changes F2L orientation?</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>UR</strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Yes</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>UF</strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>In Place /</strong></p><p><strong>Diag Slot</strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong>No</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Adj Slot</strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>","zh":"<p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">F2L色向</strong></p><p>定义：</p><p><a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>色向指F2L棱关于FB轴的色向. 棱色向定义参见\"EO\"页. 本文不包括镜像. 对所有F2L情况, R*,U*,F2不改变F2L色向, 而F*,B*会改变. 如果能观察到且公式不难, 一般优先还原色向正确的F2L来避免不必要转体.</p><p><strong>F2L色向判断方法</strong></p><p>当<a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>棱位于U层，观察棱U格和F心；</p><p>当<a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>棱位于E层，观察棱F(B)格和F心；</p><p>若它们同反色, 则<a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>色向正确，否则错误。</p><p>*为方便观察，当棱位于BL(或BR)，也可观察棱L(或R)格和L(或R)心。</p><p><strong>黄棱色向判断方法</strong></p><p>当黄棱位于U层，观察棱U格；</p><p>当黄棱位于E层，观察棱F(B)格；</p><p>若它是黄色, 则黄棱色向正确，否则错误。</p><p><strong>y转体对F2L色向的影响</strong></p><p>y2不改变任何色向;</p><p>y*不改变E层<a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>色向，改变U层F2L色向.</p><p><strong>y转体对黄棱色向的影响</strong></p><p>y*改变E层黄棱色向，不改变U层黄棱色向.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>棱位置</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>色向正确 (不需转体)</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>色向错误 (需转体)</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>y*是否会改变色向</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>UR</strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong>会</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>UF</strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>归位或对角槽</strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong>不会</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>邻槽</strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/zh/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":[],"thumb":"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-orientation/en/image2.svg","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
